01:19:15,557 --> 01:19:26,885
you, Paulette, helped to support the kindergarten aides because Medford had one of the very few extended day programs for kindergarten students at that time that was free.

477
01:19:26,985 --> 01:19:28,346
There was no charge for that.

478
01:19:29,367 --> 01:19:32,809
All of the other districts around us charged for extended day.

479
01:19:33,309 --> 01:19:34,250
Medford did not.

480
01:19:34,950 --> 01:19:44,037
