484
01:20:05,791 --> 01:20:17,958
Facebook has made that possible, yes, but it's been largely because we were able to consolidate our schools, even though it meant the loss of our beloved Hervey.

485
01:20:19,239 --> 01:20:24,963
But we understood that the little schools that we had did not have

486
01:20:26,416 --> 01:20:31,240
